thread.title: Ruler of Ajman Reviews Federal Customs Authority projects
thread.title_full: Ruler of Ajman Reviews Federal Customs Authority projects | MENAFN.COM

author: Emirates News Agency (WAM)
title: Ruler of Ajman Reviews Federal Customs Authority projects
text:
(MENAFN - Emirates News Agency (WAM)) AJMAN 11th October 2015 (WAM) -- H.H. Sheikh Humaid bin Rashid Al Nuaimi Supreme Council Member and Ruler of Ajman has reviewed the Federal Customs Authority projects plans and future strategy during a meeting today with Ali Mohamed Subaih Al Ka'abi Chairman of the UAE Federal Customs Authority FCA. 
The meeting was attended by Hamad bin Abdul Rahman Al Midfa Secretary-General of Federal Supreme Council Affairs at the Ministry of Presidential Affairs Sheikh Abdulaziz bin Humaid Al Nuaimi Chairman of Ajman Tourism Development Department H.H. Sheikh Rashid bin Humaid Al Nuaimi Chairman of Ajman Municipality and Planning Department Sheikh Mohammed bin Abdullah Al Nuaimi Chairman of Ajman Port and Customs Department and a number of officials. 
WAM/Trainee/Khulood 

WAM/Moran
